HEADWORD: Duchess
<hw>Duch"ess</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>duchesse</ets>, fr. <ets>duc</ets> duke.]</ety> <def>The wife or
widow of a duke; also, a lady who has the sovereignty of a duchy in her
own right.</def>⟦br⟧
